mainEntity.name:
Promotional Bags

Custom printed bags are one of the most popular product categories in the promotional products industry. With so many types to choose from, and serving so many purposes, choosing the right bag may seem like a daunting task.

At Identity Links, we try to make your choice a bit easier.   We have over twenty categories of promotional bags to narrow your choices.  From plastic and paper bags, to backpacks and draw string bags, we're sure to have the style and type of bag to fit your needs.

Looking for bags for a trade show or convention, or bags for your store or boutique?  We have tote bags in all shapes and sizes, in a variety of different materials, and pricing to fit any budget.
